Yoloworld segmentation results improve if a trailing comma is added.

Be wary that due to its implementation the node will throw an error if written category subjects are not found within the given image when mask_combined is false.
Inpaint Crop and Inpaint Stitch can be bypassed if desired, but not recommended.
Because we're not using the VAE Encode (for Inpainting) Node the denoise value does work to modulate the strength of our inpaint.

Can use mask editor to manually adjust segmentation results from Yoloworld if the need arises. Note that composite masks will be applied to every yolo mask when mask_combined and mask_extracted are both false. Workflow mainly intended to focus on one subject at a time anyways.

green beer bottle, glass bottle, alcohol, green bottle

Workflow is done in 2 processes with only one active for queuing at a given time.

If you prefer running the entire workflow all in one go you can either directly connect Mask group outputs to Inpaint group inputs (yellow/purple nodes respectively) or use KJNodes set/get nodes in place of receiver/sender nodes.
The extra mask list node is necessary to deal with an edge case where mask composite fails if manual masks are empty while the yolo mask is not and mask_combined and mask_extracted are both false.
